<p>What to do when your Mac forgets its window positions? Migrating iTunes to a new computer? Sending your Mac in for repair? Want to import your data from one Mac to another? Have a question of your own? No fear, your geeks&hellip; are here! John and Dave take these questions &mdash; and more&hellip; much, much more &mdash; answer and discuss them on the show. Also included in this episode are some replies to the SSD on-the-cheap concept, as well as a handful of Cool Stuff Found sent in by you and other listeners. Download today, support your two favorite geeks, and enjoy!<br /><img data-recalc-dims="1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="center" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.macobserver.com/imgs/dave/macGeekGab02.jpg?resize=230%2C230" border="0" width="230" height="230" />&nbsp;</p>
<p>Note: Shownotes are complete!</p>
